{"tid":2263810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尼斯恐襲｜馬來西亞前首相馬哈蒂爾：穆斯林有權殺數百萬法國人 Twitter急刪文","createTime":"2020-10-30T07:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T23:33:30.000Z","uid":70063,"like":98,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"b3807b22a64fb95606978f1bbe69a46c1bcc911c","tid":2263810,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201030/SWPYB7KGHJB4ZAAJBVMUH3HWHE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ok2qEFfD-ZHEv0R6YTqHDdDHmcYbxQot8yivi9d7hGUJZEYEXFQr4xpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201030%2FSWPYB7KGHJB4ZAAJBVMUH3HWHE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ok2qEFfD-ZHEv0R6YTqHDdDHmcYbxQot8yivi9d7hGUJZEYEXFQr4xpg&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=e00bda65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201030%2FSWPYB7KGHJB4ZAAJBVMUH3HWHE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ok2qEFfD-ZHEv0R6YTqHDdDHmcYbxQot8yivi9d7hGUJZEYEXFQr4xpg&h=d4952e0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201030/SWPYB7KGHJB4ZAAJBVMUH3HWHE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ok2qEFfD-ZHEv0R6YTqHDdDHmcYbxQot8yivi9d7hGUJZEYEXFQr4xpg</a><br />\n<br />\n法國尼斯周四發生懷疑伊斯蘭激進分子斬殺3人事件，馬來西亞前首相馬哈蒂爾（Mahathir Mohamad）在事發後不久說，穆斯林「有權憤怒和殺死數以百萬法國人」。馬哈蒂爾的言論引起公憤，Twitter迅速刪除他的推文。<br />\n<br />\n馬哈蒂爾一向反對西方文化，近日批評法國總統馬克龍拒絕譴責展示伊斯蘭教先知穆罕默德漫畫的行為。他在Twitter發文說：「馬克龍沒有展示其文明，他譴責伊斯蘭教和穆斯林殺死侮辱伊斯蘭教先知的教師，是很幼稚，這不符伊斯蘭教義。」<br />\n<br />\n他又說：「但不論宗教，憤怒的人就會殺人。法國的歷史中也曾殺害數以百萬計的人，不少是穆斯林...穆斯林有權憤怒，也有權殺死數以百萬法國人，以報過往大屠殺之仇。」<br />\n<br />\n馬哈蒂爾認為西方不應把思想與價值強加其他人之上，「這樣做是剝奪他人的自由」。馬來西亞有人口超過3200萬，其中61%信奉伊斯蘭教。<br />\n<br />\n一名男子周四持刀闖入尼斯聖母院教堂大開殺戒，至少造成3人死亡及數人受傷，死者包括兩名女性及一名男性，其中一名女子頭被斬下。尼斯市長稱疑犯一直不斷大叫「真主偉大」(Allahu akbar! )。這已是法國兩個月來第3宗襲擊事件。"},{"pid":"5b51f84b9436ed6fc431cea1f700bf56bcb00401","tid":2263810,"uid":52215,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"Allahu Akbar"},{"pid":"e098b28446a6eab85ee8a82f58f3ebff3b61f379","tid":2263810,"uid":295230,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>馬哈蒂爾認為西方不應把思想與價值強加其他人之上，「這樣做是剝奪他人的自由」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊解我覺得由佢把口講出黎好諷刺既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457792700951744909c8c950ff21b45651f76e09","tid":2263810,"uid":99962,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"唔怪得佢同維尼熊總司令唔岩啦"},{"pid":"a11c59d8e67bba1601a50006fecb02a921f0938f","tid":2263810,"uid":295230,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"呢條死垃圾就係馬來西亞原教旨主義咁盛行既主要推手之一"},{"pid":"cc0a2cb0ba9375448fd6e65d73e60d24f21370fa","tid":2263810,"uid":121146,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"想問Twitter刪黎做乜鳩? 佢E D仆街言論係應該全世界都知"},{"pid":"9be2af1fb9fbf51246c3f7d047fc2a8521bd8605","tid":2263810,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"想再次敗部復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n借原教旨主義&nbsp;打倒政敵?"},{"pid":"e37a3dda50104c35d90d8dd9fadd534e7276f5bb","tid":2263810,"uid":118120,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"其實所有穆斯林都覺得殺死異教徒係理所當然, <br />\n就算受過教育既都係咁諗<br />\n只係差在有冇講出口,  呢個前首相就係例子"},{"pid":"501604277010f7e1dcb4a2033eb4